729756f-b.title: Richmond: Tompkins Avenue - Clifton Avenue
729756f-b.text:
(1)
Tompkins Avenue, east side, north from Clifton
Avenue. In the left backaround is St. Josephs Roman
Catholic Church, at the N. E. corner of St. Mary's
Avenue.
January 18, 1931
P. i. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
A detail view of the N. E. corner of Tomokins
and Clifton Avenues, showing the Lvric Theatre, a
movie house.
January 18, 193i
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
